'''Arvid David Hummel''' (30 April 1778, [[Göteborg]] – 20 October 1836, [[Ekenäs, Finland|Ekenäs]]) was a [[Sweden|Swedish]] [[entomologist]].

Hummel was a [[Civil law notary|notary]]. He wrote ''Essais entomologiques''. St. Pétersbourg: de l'Imprimerie de la Chancellerie privée du Ministère de l'Intérieur, 1821–29.

==References==
