{{Infobox scientist | name = Hugo Erich Meyer von Klinggräff | image = <!--(filename only)--> | image_size = | alt = | caption = | birth_date = {{Birth date|1820|06|07}} | birth_place = [[Klein Watkowitz]], Stuhm | death_date = {{Death date and age|1902|04|03|1820|06|07}} | death_place = [[Paleschken]], Stuhm | resting_place = | resting_place_coordinates = <!-- {{Coord|LAT|LONG|type:landmark|display=inline,title}} --> | residence = | citizenship = German | nationality = German | fields = [[bryology]] | workplaces = | alma_mater = [[University of Königsberg]] | thesis_title = | thesis_url = | thesis_year = | doctoral_advisor = | academic_advisors = | doctoral_students = | notable_students = | known_for = | author_abbrev_bot = | author_abbrev_zoo = | influences = | influenced = | awards = | signature = <!--(filename only)--> | signature_alt = | website = <!-- {{URL|www.example.com}} --> | footnotes = | spouse = }} '''Hugo Erich Meyer von Klinggräff''' (7 June 1820 in [[Klein Watkowitz]], Stuhm &ndash; 3 April 1902 in [[Paleschken]], Stuhm) was a German botanist specialist of [[bryophyte]]s. He was the brother of botanist [[Carl Julius Meyer von Klinggräff]], with whom he often collaborated.
In 1826, he moved with his parents to a homestead located not far from [[Zagreb|Agram]], [[Croatia]]. He later studied at the [[University of Königsberg]], receiving his doctorate in 1846. Following graduation, he returned to Croatia, where he botanized in areas along the [[Adriatic Sea]] and islands within the [[Gulf of Quarnero]]. During this time period, he collaborated with other botanists, that included [[Mutius von Tommasini]]. In 1852 he acquired an estate in Wiszniewo bei Lobau, [[Province of Prussia]].<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=Sdg5AAAAIAAJ&pg=RA1-PA2 Bericht, Volumes 26-32] by Westpreussischer botanisch-zoologischer Verein</ref><ref>[http://www.sysbot.biologie.uni-muenchen.de/botsyst/ic/ic-bry-k.htm Bryophytes K] (Collectors Index Herbarium M)</ref>
{{botanist|H.Klinggr.}}
== Publications == * Klinggräff, H. v. (1858) "Die höheren Cryptogamen Preussens" (Königsberg) – The higher [[cryptogam]]s of Prussia. * "Die in der Umgegend von Agram in Croatien vorkommenden Pflanzen", 1861 – On plants native to areas near Agram. * "Versuch einer topographischen Flora der Provinz Westpreussen" 1880 – Essay on the [[phytogeography]] of West Prussia.<ref>[https://openlibrary.org/search?author_key=OL2399288A&first_publish_year=1880 Open Library] Versuch einer topographischen Flora der Provinz Westpreussen</ref> * "Ueber die bastarde bei farnen und moosen", 1889 – On hybrids of [[fern]]s and mosses.<ref>[https://www.google.com/search?tbo=p&tbm=bks&q=inauthor:%22Hugo+von+Klinggr%C3%A4ff%22&gws_rd=ssl Google Books] published works</ref> * "Die leber- und laubmoose West- und Ostpreussens, 1893 – [[Liverwort]]s and [[moss]]es of [[West Prussia|West]] and [[East Prussia]].<ref>[http://classify.oclc.org/classify2/ClassifyDemo?search-author-txt=%22Klinggr%C3%A4ff%2C+Hugo+Erich+Meyer+von%2C+1820-1902%22 OCLC Classify] published works</ref>
